dual on\/off switches and anti-surge)<\/li>\n<li>Desk lamps<\/li>\n<li>Hand tools<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<div>Items on the list will get crossed out as we get enough of them in, so that we don&#8217;t have storage issues. Thanks in advance!<\/div>\n<p>Please use the donation form below if you&#8217;re willing to donate: (some browsers have trouble with it so here&#8217;s an alternative:\u00a0<a title=\"The Great Farset Labs Donation Form\" href=\"https:\/\/docs.google.com\/a\/andrewbolster.info\/spreadsheet\/viewform?formkey=dDJRanJpZTlPTW9VN3VLbWtWRllibGc6MQ\" target=\"_blank\">link<\/a>.)<\/p>\n<p><iframe src=\"https:\/\/docs.google.com\/spreadsheet\/embeddedform?formkey=dDJRanJpZTlPTW9VN3VLbWtWRllibGc6MQ\" frameborder=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" marginheight=\"0\" width=\"760\" height=\"960\"><\/iframe><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>We very much appreciate the donations that we&#8217;ve already received &#8211; without the community, Farset Labs doesn&#8217;t exist, so it&#8217;s great to see people supporting us. What we&#8217;re seeing however are some pretty big-ticket items, which is great, but we also need the small stuff. Grouped together, the items that are listed below are pretty [&hellip;]<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":3,"featured_media":154,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"footnotes":""},"categories":[139,1],"tags":[81,82,57,83,80],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/blog.farsetlabs.org.uk\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/143"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/blog.farsetlabs.org.uk\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/blog.farsetlabs.org.uk\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/blog.farsetlabs.org.uk\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/3"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/blog.farsetlabs.org.uk\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=143"}],"version-history":[{"count":8,"href":"https:\/\/blog.farsetlabs.org.uk\/wp-js